Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:32.44,0:01:34.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為了救助破爛不堪的White Base
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:34.97,0:01:41.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由聯邦軍派出的米迪亞運輸部隊\N遭到了古夫和德太轟炸機的襲擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:46.84,0:01:48.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,得知緊急情況的阿姆羅他們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:49.01,0:01:53.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,借助著為強化GUNDAM而帶來的G部件的幫助殲滅了敵人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:05.91,0:02:12.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,『迫擊！三連星德姆』
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:12.80,0:02:14.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是說笑吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:15.10,0:02:16.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們這麼說，簡直豈有此理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:17.14,0:02:19.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在地球聯邦軍包圍下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:20.14,0:02:23.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,馬·克貝曾送了很多礦物資源來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:24.51,0:02:26.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而運輸艦所用及MS所用也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:26.58,0:02:29.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起，這樣便會失去ZION權威
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:32.25,0:02:34.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,失去ZION的權威？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:34.59,0:02:37.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為了打勝，就算失去你們的自尊那又有什麼關係？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:38.59,0:02:40.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到時我會補償給你們的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:41.93,0:02:43.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,將在地球使用過的新型MS
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:44.27,0:02:46.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,運過去給夏亞使用吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.60,0:02:48.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，現在的情況...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:48.64,0:02:50.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我說現在就要送過去！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.64,0:02:52.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,當然，夏亞現在前去北愛爾蘭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:52.34,0:02:57.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以，現在分佈於各部隊的MS
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.65,0:02:59.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也應該集合到地球作戰才對！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:00.55,0:03:02.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們調動一些MS過來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.29,0:03:05.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,將多姆也送過去吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.12,0:03:09.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是！我會下命令了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.66,0:03:11.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到時叫他們和馬·克貝上校會合吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.23,0:03:16.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那就好了！做事要隨機應變呢！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.57,0:03:19.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,佔領了月球的基希莉亞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.60,0:03:23.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,根本沒可能親自到地球作戰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.27,0:03:26.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為地球上各區戰況很不穩定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.68,0:03:28.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在她可以做的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.18,0:03:30.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,便將善戰的勇士黑色三連星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.91,0:03:35.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在敖德薩計劃前派去助馬·克貝參戰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.04,0:03:57.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,早晨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.21,0:04:00.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,早晨，瑪吉露達少尉！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.41,0:04:04.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是？可以給GUNDAM充電的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.78,0:04:08.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因要自己修理，所以預先整理好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.55,0:04:09.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿姆羅，你真行！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.99,0:04:11.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你想去那裏？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.55,0:04:12.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想去控制室！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.12,0:04:13.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那不如由我帶你去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.00,0:04:14.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.89,0:04:16.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要緊，我可以帶你走快捷方式
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.13,0:04:17.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,省回點時間啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.02,0:04:18.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,麻煩你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:30.84,0:04:32.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,早晨！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.44,0:04:32.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,早晨！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.96,0:04:34.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿姆囉！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.32,0:04:35.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,又做什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.58,0:04:40.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不是說過在飯後會幫我修理空氣調節器的嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.85,0:04:41.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.25,0:04:43.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你真過份了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.72,0:04:45.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真過份！真過份！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.32,0:04:49.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我覺得瑪吉露達少尉如我的夢中情人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.26,0:04:51.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,做事又能幹，人又溫柔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.73,0:04:55.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,若我也有樣的女朋友就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.33,0:04:57.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你似乎很空閒呢！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.70,0:05:03.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,早晨！瑪吉露達少尉！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.87,0:05:05.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你想找女朋友嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.04,0:05:08.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,少尉，被你聽到真害羞呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.88,0:05:11.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過...可以和我拍張照嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.55,0:05:13.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是我個人小小的願望！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.75,0:05:15.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好的，現在就拍照吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.79,0:05:16.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是，多謝你！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.56,0:05:21.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們竟然這麼多人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.66,0:05:23.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一架相機怎拍得下呢！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.84,0:05:25.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要緊吧！凱！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.26,0:05:27.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好！我要拍照了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.57,0:05:40.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,布萊特，我帶了瑪吉露達少尉來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.61,0:05:41.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是辛苦你呢！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.18,0:05:43.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣就可以了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.68,0:05:44.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起，少尉！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.38,0:05:46.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你似乎精神好了很多！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:46.92,0:05:47.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我先出去了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:06.64,0:06:08.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我覺得推進的速度實在太慢了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.90,0:06:11.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原本還想提早敖德薩計劃...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.54,0:06:14.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,艾少將，快叫他們盡快集合吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.31,0:06:15.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是...不過...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.68,0:06:18.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別嚕囌了，快照我說的去做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.65,0:06:19.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.98,0:06:22.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雷比爾將軍，這是空軍巡邏隊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.89,0:06:24.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在空中所收集到的情報來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.55,0:06:27.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,ZION贊斯巴爾母艦降落到地球嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:28.92,0:06:32.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,其實這件事我們一早已知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.66,0:06:34.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過...問題卻在後面！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.90,0:06:38.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們帶來了黑色三連星及嶄新的MS來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.30,0:06:42.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在魯姆戰役中，我就是被他們所俘虜的了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.67,0:06:44.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這班人相當難對付...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.57,0:06:48.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,唯有提早敖德薩計劃了，艾少將
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.01,0:06:52.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是！我立即通知各部隊單位
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.18,0:06:55.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼你的臉色都蒼白了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.02,0:06:58.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,舒特拉，到底你是否雙重間諜？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.85,0:07:01.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為何黑色三連星及贊斯巴爾的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.56,0:07:03.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這麼快就給雷比爾將軍知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:03.53,0:07:05.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不會吧，沒可能的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:06.45,0:07:09.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你去通知馬·克貝上校說敖德薩作戰提早開始\N叫他及早預防吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.11,0:07:10.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.94,0:07:14.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們能否及早完成呢？大偉！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.10,0:07:16.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是，我看可以的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.21,0:07:19.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,早一點助阿姆羅增加GUNDAM的能力！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.28,0:07:20.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.04,0:07:25.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,瑪吉露達少尉，為何你會參加補給部隊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.58,0:07:28.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為...戰爭中只有破壞行動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.25,0:07:32.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,唯有補給隊算是生產物品的希望
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.89,0:07:34.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可能是這個原因吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.56,0:07:35.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,生產物品...？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.30,0:07:40.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然戰爭都是破壞性
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.90,0:07:43.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果人類只有破壞便難以生存了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.23,0:07:45.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以要有生產才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.07,0:07:48.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好了，已經洗淨了放射能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.58,0:07:55.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,瑪吉露達少尉...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.05,0:07:59.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我時常也這麼想的...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.85,0:08:03.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,瑪吉露達少尉是個堅強的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.85,0:08:07.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你千萬別亂說呢！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.62,0:08:09.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.01,0:08:10.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要緊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.60,0:08:20.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,包在我身上吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.47,0:08:23.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你怎可用夏亞和我們比較呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.14,0:08:27.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我很想看木馬和白色傢伙到底有多厲害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.73,0:08:29.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,????
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.81,0:08:31.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,奧狄、波斯我們去！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.81,0:08:32.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.49,0:08:43.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很快便接近他們了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.54,0:08:56.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,發現有金屬反應
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.01,0:08:58.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,繞去山那邊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.59,0:09:14.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.67,0:09:16.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有三架敵軍MS！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:16.63,0:09:18.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由2點鐘方向入侵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:18.59,0:09:19.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,採取緊急戒備！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.93,0:09:21.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,米萊，拜託你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:21.20,0:09:21.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.53,0:09:23.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,敵人來了！敵人來了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.77,0:09:28.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,將三部運輸機放在前面抵擋敵軍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.54,0:09:33.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然有說明書可解決問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:33.61,0:09:35.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是我一個不知行不行的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.71,0:09:38.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,隼人，你沒問題嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.75,0:09:40.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我和凱你不是一個人駕駛嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:40.72,0:09:41.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家也一樣的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:48.22,0:09:49.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,進入第二監視網
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.63,0:09:50.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,移動速度非常之快！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.76,0:09:52.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,GUNDAM情況又如何？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.30,0:09:55.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他現在正檢查G戰機
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.90,0:09:57.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且還叫我去試試呢！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.00,0:09:59.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,誰叫你的？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.57,0:10:02.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是技師隊長大偉，他說我可駕駛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.60,0:10:04.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼會的？亞中不行嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:04.94,0:10:06.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他也算是個駕駛員啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.38,0:10:07.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他說一定要駕駛過MS才行的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.24,0:10:12.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那我叫芙勞·波代替你的位置好嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.58,0:10:14.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,米萊，起動軸有問題！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.58,0:10:16.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,叫大家注意高度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.92,0:10:17.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:17.92,0:10:19.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,芙勞·波，拜託了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.76,0:10:20.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我走了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:24.76,0:10:26.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有關連接部分，有計算機控制的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:27.26,0:10:28.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,駕駛員可以不用理會！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.66,0:10:30.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，計算機被破壞怎算？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.67,0:10:33.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只有電磁平整器就會自動結合
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.54,0:10:37.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過時間要在六百里以上，否則會掉下來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.98,0:10:39.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為何G戰機駕駛員還未到來？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.15,0:10:40.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:41.18,0:10:41.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要快些呢！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:41.83,0:10:42.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:47.88,0:10:49.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這架就是G戰機了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.99,0:10:51.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我記得它是叫G戰機的...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.72,0:10:53.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不懂控制的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.96,0:10:56.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只要你坐過一次便會明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.73,0:10:59.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們要對這武器有信心！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:59.96,0:11:01.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我會在控制室內看著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.28,0:11:02.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:06.57,0:11:08.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雪拉，你準備好嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:08.37,0:11:10.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我還未檢查的，再等一會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:13.91,0:11:15.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那傢伙的速度真快！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.35,0:11:22.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,引擎動力一直不能加高！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:22.92,0:11:23.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎樣也提升不了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.25,0:11:25.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那找專家來看吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.27,0:11:26.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:27.06,0:11:30.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,芙勞·波，叫瑪吉露達少尉和大偉技師來！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:30.73,0:11:32.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,母艦發生什麼事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.92,0:11:34.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為何不起飛？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:34.30,0:11:36.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為引擎的動力不能提高
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.40,0:11:38.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼？大偉！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.60,0:11:40.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,芙勞·波，阿姆羅、雪拉、G戰機如何？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.54,0:11:43.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雪拉現在還未行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:43.71,0:11:45.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他說不知道如何控制GUNDAM的結合
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.88,0:11:49.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那不重要，叫他交給阿姆羅處理吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.88,0:11:53.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒問題，G戰機可以的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.39,0:11:53.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:54.08,0:11:56.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,G戰機、阿姆羅、雪拉，出發
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:56.26,0:11:56.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:56.86,0:11:58.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿姆羅、雪拉現在出發！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:59.62,0:12:02.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,連接系統是第1，第2是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:02.89,0:12:03.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雪拉，我們出發了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:04.23,0:12:05.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是！隨便！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:06.06,0:12:08.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,準備開大引擎，對好發動軸了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.80,0:12:09.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,OK！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.18,0:12:29.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在左面！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.96,0:12:35.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,受死吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:41.53,0:12:42.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,糟了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.36,0:13:06.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雪拉，往左面去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.70,0:13:17.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雪拉，結合時由你控制比較易的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:18.23,0:13:20.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拜託了，較好紅外線控制器可以嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.04,0:13:22.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由我來發射G戰機主炮！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.04,0:13:24.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在那裏？敵人呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.97,0:13:27.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在後面來呢！快回轉！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:27.63,0:13:28.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.38,0:13:29.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,盡量拉住控制捍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:31.91,0:13:33.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,用力點！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.59,0:13:42.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,糟了！可能會撞上！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:44.03,0:13:45.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太遲了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:45.33,0:13:46.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,糟了，很難急速回轉上！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:47.20,0:13:49.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過G戰機的雷射炮熱能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:49.70,0:13:51.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,比GUNDAM強三倍以上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:51.56,0:13:52.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要想辦法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:52.87,0:13:56.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,190度回轉，準備雷射炮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.61,0:13:57.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:58.01,0:13:59.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒錯，在40度角左右
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:03.21,0:14:04.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好，發射！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:07.35,0:14:08.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,呀，好險呢！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.06,0:14:19.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好像從未見過呢！完全沒有資料！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:24.50,0:14:27.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有點像戰機，但以前未見過啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.37,0:14:32.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,差一點，再來一次，要加回度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.74,0:14:38.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到你們看看我的厲害了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.18,0:14:42.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,發動機本身是沒問題的，真奇怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.38,0:14:43.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我這邊也是一樣！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.19,0:14:45.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,重新檢查過吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.59,0:14:46.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,G戰機正在艱苦作戰！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.19,0:14:49.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,鋼坦克和鋼加農正在後退
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:49.62,0:14:50.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎辦？瑪吉露達少尉！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.99,0:14:53.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要緊，大偉會修好它的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.66,0:14:58.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,芙勞·波，麻煩你通知我的運輸機隨時準備出戰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.51,0:14:59.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:00.00,0:15:02.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看來已太遲了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.94,0:15:04.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為何你有這想法？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:04.87,0:15:07.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也不知...但...有這種感覺！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.04,0:15:10.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:12.25,0:15:12.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒有！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:17.22,0:15:19.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你似乎很緊張呢！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.92,0:15:21.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.25,0:15:23.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但不由你不緊張的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.89,0:15:28.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿姆羅、雪拉、凱、隼人加油啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:31.23,0:15:32.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是在這裏嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:37.91,0:15:41.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我真沒用，連阻止敵人也不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.91,0:15:45.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡極了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:54.26,0:15:54.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雪拉！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.11,0:15:55.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒事的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.19,0:15:56.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,敵人呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:57.00,0:15:58.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們前進了很多！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.29,0:16:00.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不如到山邊避一避吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:00.86,0:16:01.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你想換裝成GUNDAM嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:01.69,0:16:02.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:02.66,0:16:04.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不知我能否控制得了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:04.87,0:16:06.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你一定可以的，雪拉！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:07.54,0:16:09.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雪拉，你不是經常說這樣的嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:10.04,0:16:13.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在輪到你了，阿姆囉！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.74,0:16:17.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,G戰機轉換成全自動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:18.08,0:16:19.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,弄錯了就糟糕！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.36,0:16:21.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不會有問題的，開始吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:28.56,0:16:33.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,4...3...2...1...0...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:41.57,0:16:43.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒有問題嗎？雪拉！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:45.57,0:16:47.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,計算機已成為我全做妥了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:48.04,0:16:50.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,成功了！阿姆羅快回母艦吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:50.71,0:16:51.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:53.58,0:16:55.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,運輸機...！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:00.99,0:17:02.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,難道是...瑪吉露達少尉？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:03.39,0:17:05.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,三號稍為升高了一些
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:05.25,0:17:06.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,????
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:06.43,0:17:07.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,????
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:08.10,0:17:11.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原因已知道了，請再等三分鐘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:11.33,0:17:12.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,二分鐘可以完成了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:18.61,0:17:21.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,主炮，水平方向發射！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:22.21,0:17:23.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有敵軍MS嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:25.68,0:17:28.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在那邊，不會再讓你胡來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:36.56,0:17:38.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,打他不中，還被他閃開了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:43.27,0:17:44.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,被他閃躲了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:46.84,0:17:48.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,糟了，母艦有危險！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:52.57,0:17:54.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聯邦軍的MS
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:54.84,0:17:56.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有點本事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:04.59,0:18:06.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,差少許便可修好母艦了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:07.19,0:18:09.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在怎可又讓他們來破壞的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.66,0:18:12.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,起航，準備！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:12.75,0:18:13.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:19.43,0:18:22.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,糟了，敵軍想先炸母艦！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.14,0:18:27.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這駕駛員真不簡單呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:27.64,0:18:31.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,奧狄、波斯，用噴射雷電攻擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:37.95,0:18:39.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,敵方的MS吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:39.49,0:18:40.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們掩護我！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:43.16,0:18:44.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那些傢伙來了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:03.58,0:19:06.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎樣，再來一次吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:10.65,0:19:12.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,運輸機？誰在裏面？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:14.59,0:19:15.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:19.73,0:19:20.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,糟了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:27.94,0:19:29.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊！這樣也可沒事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:38.35,0:19:40.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再這樣下去就...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:43.62,0:19:45.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,豈有此理，差點便幹掉他了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:21.49,0:20:23.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎會？怎會這樣的？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:27.26,0:20:29.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,波斯的多姆給打敗了！
